_:Nb9d8b6746a114e09aa35397d948074bf <http://schema.org/text> "This notice sets out how and why we will use your personal data, and your rights, if you’re in contact with the Government Office for Technology Transfer. " .
_:Ne6fe75912ec343aa820568bc26492556 <http://schema.org/itemListElement> _:N960177791b784f14b2daf3410eb9e954 .
_:Nb9d8b6746a114e09aa35397d948074bf <http://schema.org/dateModified> "2022-10-04T17:33:54+01:00"^^<http://schema.org/Date> .
