_:Nb9d8b6746a114e09aa35397d948074bf <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> .
